trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of SharePoint project items.
trans-unit.target: 表示 SharePoint 项目项的集合。

trans-unit.source: The name of SharePoint project item to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的名称。

trans-unit.source: The type ID of the SharePoint project item to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的类型 ID。

trans-unit.source: Creates and adds a new instance of a SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 创建并添加 SharePoint 项目项的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the SharePoint project item that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的 SharePoint 项目项的实例。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if any of the arguments are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当任一参数为 <see langword="null" /> 时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs in the following cases:
trans-unit.target: 在以下情况下发生：

trans-unit.source: If any of the parameters are empty strings.
trans-unit.target: 如果任一参数为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: If a SharePoint project item with the provided name already exists.
trans-unit.target: 如果已存在具有所提供名称的 SharePoint 项目项。

trans-unit.source: The name of a SharePoint project item to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的名称。

trans-unit.source: The type ID of the SharePoint project item to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的类型 ID。

trans-unit.source: Skips auto-add to a first available feature if <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果为 <see langword="true" />，则跳过自动添加，转到第一个可用功能。

trans-unit.source: Creates and adds a new instance of SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 创建并添加 SharePoint 项目项的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the SharePoint project item that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的 SharePoint 项目项的实例。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if any of the arguments are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当任一参数为 <see langword="null" /> 时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs in the following cases:
trans-unit.target: 在以下情况下发生：

trans-unit.source: If any of the parameters are empty strings.
trans-unit.target: 如果任一参数为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: If a SharePoint project item with the provided name already exists.
trans-unit.target: 如果已存在具有所提供名称的 SharePoint 项目项。

trans-unit.source: The subfolder in the project where the new SharePoint item is created.
trans-unit.target: 项目中创建新的 SharePoint 项的子文件夹。

trans-unit.source: The name of SharePoint project item to be added.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的名称。

trans-unit.source: The type ID of the SharePoint project item to be added.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的 SharePoint 项目项的类型 ID。

trans-unit.source: Creates and adds a new instance of SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 创建并添加 SharePoint 项目项的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the SharePoint project item that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的 SharePoint 项目项的实例。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if any of the arguments are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当任一参数为 <see langword="null" /> 时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs in the following cases:
trans-unit.target: 在以下情况下发生：

trans-unit.source: If any of the parameters are empty strings.
trans-unit.target: 如果任一参数为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: If the path is not a valid absolute path (that is, not under the project root path).
trans-unit.target: 如果路径不是有效的绝对路径（即不在项目根路径下）。

trans-unit.source: If a SharePoint project item with the provided name already exists.
trans-unit.target: 如果已存在具有所提供名称的 SharePoint 项目项。

trans-unit.source: The base path of the project item.
trans-unit.target: 项目项的基路径。

trans-unit.source: Can be either relative to the project path or absolute.
trans-unit.target: 可以是相对项目路径，也可以是绝对项目路径。

trans-unit.source: The name of the project item.
trans-unit.target: 项目项的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name should be file system-friendly.
trans-unit.target: 名称应该为文件系统友好型。

trans-unit.source: The type of the project item.
trans-unit.target: 项目项的类型。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="true" />, the project system will not automatically add a feature or package for the project item.
trans-unit.target: 如果为 <see langword="true" />，项目系统不会自动添加项目项的功能或包。

trans-unit.source: Creates and adds a SharePoint project item to the project.
trans-unit.target: 创建 SharePoint 项目项，并将其添加到项目。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the new project item.
trans-unit.target: 新项目项的实例。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if any of the arguments are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当任一参数为 <see langword="null" /> 时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs in the following cases:
trans-unit.target: 在以下情况下发生：

trans-unit.source: If any of the parameters are empty strings.
trans-unit.target: 如果任一参数为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: If the path is not a valid absolute path (that is, not under the project root path).
trans-unit.target: 如果路径不是有效的绝对路径（即不在项目根路径下）。

trans-unit.source: If a SharePoint project item with the provided name already exists.
trans-unit.target: 如果已存在具有所提供名称的 SharePoint 项目项。

trans-unit.source: The ID of the SharePoint project item instance to find.
trans-unit.target: 要查找的 SharePoint 项目项实例的 ID。

trans-unit.source: Finds a <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> instance by its ID.
trans-unit.target: 按其 ID 查找 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 实例。

trans-unit.source: An object representing the SharePoint project item instance if it found; <see langword="null" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到，则为表示 SharePoint 项目项实例的对象；否则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> folder path.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 文件夹路径。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> by its folder path.
trans-unit.target: 按其文件夹路径获取 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 的实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of a SharePoint project item if it is found; <see langword="null" /> or <see langword="Nothing" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果它找到，则 SharePoint 项目项的实例<see langword="null" />或<see langword="Nothing" />否则为。

trans-unit.source: `folderPath` can be either an absolute folder path or a relative path to the project folder.
trans-unit.target: `folderPath` 可以是绝对文件夹路径或项目文件夹的相对路径。

trans-unit.source: Gets the project instance owning this collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取拥有此集合的项目实例。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a project instance.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个项目实例的对象。
